seo: Dlink_DCS信息泄露漏洞,CVE-2020-25078,高危漏洞,信息泄露
summary: 该插件用于检测Dlink_DCS设备是否存在CVE-2020-25078信息泄露漏洞，通过发送特定HTTP请求检查返回的数据中是否包含用户名、密码等敏感信息。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether Dlink_DCS devices have the CVE-2020-25078 information leak vulnerability by sending a specific HTTP request and checking if the returned data contains sensitive information such as usernames and passwords.
